{"data":[{"date":"19:21 29/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 29/6: M.U mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/25/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-296-mu-muon-chieu-mo-sao-tuyen-duc-chelsea-sap-co-bom-tan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d, Real Madrid mua sao AC Milan,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 29/6</h2><h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo\u00a0th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd AS, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi G\u0110\u0110H Ed Woodward v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft Toni Kroos v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a M.U, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1t huy m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2022 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 l\u00e0 500 tri\u1ec7u euro. Tuy nhi\u00ean Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 296 MU mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 296 MU mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Toni-Kroos.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9\u00a0Toni Kroos t\u1eeb Real Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Aleksandr Golovin trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Nga \u1edf World Cup, BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia cho bi\u1ebft Juventus c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Golovin, tuy nhi\u00ean, Bianconeri ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 20 tri\u1ec7u euro, trong khi CSKA mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 25 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal s\u0103n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ronaldo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo The Sun, hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh l\u00e0 M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\u00a0l\u00e0 William Carvalho trong h\u00e8 t\u1edbi. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 cao tu\u1ed5i tuy nhi\u00ean Carvalho v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn b\u1edfi anh \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p, sau khi b\u1ecb c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n, Sporting Lisbon thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110T Brazil<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Metro m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 The Blues g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker c\u1ee7a AS Roma. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Thibaut Courtois v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ra \u0111i, Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alisson, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch b\u00e1n Courtois v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a The Blues.</p>\r\n<h2>M.U h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Martial<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Martial kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n thi\u1ebft tha vi\u1ec7c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho M.U, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n anh trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n Martial ra \u0111i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb m\u1ea1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo\u00a0Sky Sports, M.U s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Anthony Martial v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 CLB Juventus l\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid mua sao AC Milan<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Marca, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Suso \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i AC Milan. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Suso t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i U19 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Inter Milan t\u1eebng h\u1ecfi mua d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>M.U, Juventus c\u1ea1nh tranh sao Real<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia\u00a0\u0111a\u0303 c\u00f4ng khai y\u0301 \u0111i\u0323nh mu\u00f4\u0301n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0323c r\u1eddi\u00a0Real Madrid \u0111\u00ea\u0309 ti\u0300m ki\u00ea\u0301m c\u01a1 h\u00f4\u0323i thi \u0111\u00e2\u0301u nhi\u00ea\u0300u h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho t\u00f4i n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Real Madrid\", Mateo Kovacic chia se\u0309. \"T\u00f4i y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf \u0111\u00f3\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, M.U v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3892","checkdouble":"189959"},{"date":"06:05 30/06","title":"Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 n\u1ebfu\u2026","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/griezmann-se-chuyen-toi-giai-nha-nghe-my-neu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Antoine Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 sau khi anh x\u00f3a \u0111i n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 Champions League v\u00e0 World Cup.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>N\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League c\u00f9ng Atletico Madrid \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Marseille, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, Griezmann \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Atletico, ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Barcelona hay m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u hi\u1ebfm hoi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Griezmann c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i CLB l\u1eabn \u0110TQG. Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2015/16, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f9ng Atletico th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Sau \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Euro 2016, anh l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Griezmann-se-chuyen-toi-giai-Nha-nghe-My-MLS-trong-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Griezmann m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 MLS</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGriezmann \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng Atletico v\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac chu\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1998. Sau \u0111\u00f3, theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, Griezmann s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m sang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7, ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng?\u201d, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Le Figaro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00f3 ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i MLS v\u00e0o khi n\u00e0o, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Khi t\u00f4i g\u1ea7n 32 hay 33 tu\u1ed5i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Griezmann \u0111ang c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 g\u1eb7p Argentina v\u00e0o 21h t\u1ed1i nay (30/6).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-dt-phap-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-lionel-messi-421-189970.html\">Sao \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina-465-189933.html\">Samuel Umtiti: \u0110T Argentina kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-phap-canh-bao-dung-hy-vong-mot-messi-cua-barcelona-o-argentina-421-189897.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o: \u201c\u0110\u1eebng hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t Messi c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u1edf Argentina\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-phap-vs-dan-mach-hoa-nhat-man-ru-ngu-o-luzhniki-421-189692.html\">Ph\u00e1p b\u1eaft tay \u0110an M\u1ea1ch h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t: \u0110i\u1ec7u ru ng\u1ee7 \u1edf Luzhniki</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-len-tieng-sau-tran-hoa-00-truoc-dan-mach-421-189682.html\">HLV \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3891","checkdouble":"189972"},{"date":"06:29 30/06","title":"\u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba\u201d t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, Barca m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/25/nguoi-thua-toa-sang-tai-world-cup-barca-mung-tham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mina t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, \u0110T Colombia b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o. \u0110\u00fang nh\u1eefng l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh d\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan v\u00e0 Senegal. \u1ede c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3, Yerry Mina \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Mina m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan, gi\u00fap Colombia tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 chung cu\u1ed9c. K\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh trung v\u1ec7 23 cao 1m95 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/yerry-mina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u l\u00e0m C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Senegal. Trong th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Colombia, c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Barcelona l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nBarca m\u1eebng v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia t\u1ea1i CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Barcelona. Barca vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina song l\u00e0 b\u1edfi l\u00fd do ngo\u00e0i chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. Trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Ernesto Valverde tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Yerry Mina\" title=\"trung ve Yerry Mina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/yerry-mina-khong-noi-nen-loi-sau-man-ra-mat-la-liga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Thomas Vermaelen. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Mina v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca. Ho\u1eb7c h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t anh, ho\u1eb7c s\u1ebd cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u00e2n Barca nh\u01b0 Sport hay Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c Mina. Song h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Blaugrana tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn h\u01a1n khi b\u00e1n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nFenerbahce l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1edbi Mina. Nh\u01b0ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng b\u1edfi hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng th\u0103ng hoa, \u0111\u1ed9 \u201chot\u201d c\u1ee7a anh l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng d\u00e2ng cao.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia-180-189646.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-va-real-dai-chien-vi-sao-bayern-munich-180-189512.html\">Barca v\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-va-real-muon-mua-thiago-alcantara-180-189489.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca vs Real v\u00ec sao tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3890","checkdouble":"189973"},{"date":"19:44 29/06","title":"G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng mua Willian, Barca v\u1eabn b\u1ecb Chelsea kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/23/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge m\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i HLV Ernesto Valverde, Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0 c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y an t\u00e2m cho m\u00f9a t\u1edbi 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Barca ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i. Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f2n m\u1ecfng khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Barca t\u1ecf ra m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi AS Roma \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League d\u00f9 th\u1eafng 4-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/30/Chelsea-khong-ban-Willian-cho-Barca-du-nhan-50-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Andres Iniesta c\u0169ng th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Barca c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Blaugrana nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea. H\u1ecd tin s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Philippe Coutinho tr\u00ean \u0110T Brazil s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWillian d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1edbt l\u1edd m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 nh\u01b0 Barcelona. Nghe \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Barca. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia c\u0169ng m\u1edbi g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian\" title=\"Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/23/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca. H\u1ecd ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng do c\u00f2n \u0111\u1eafn \u0111o gi\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m Antonio Conte v\u00e0 Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a Napoli. Chelsea ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau khi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWillian s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2020, t\u1ee9c sau \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u The Blues kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil song theo gi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c. S\u1ee9c h\u00fat t\u1eeb Barca r\u1ed3i Man United c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Willian ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau Christian Pulisic (Borussia Dortmund), Chelsea \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Aleksandr Golovin c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang n\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 c\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Nga.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/atletico-madrid-bat-ngo-muon-hut-mau-chelsea-172-189844.html\">Atletico Madrid b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n h\u00fat m\u00e1u Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/trung-ve-tri-gia-88-trieu-bang-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-chelsea-172-189829.html\">Trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-giai-cuu-david-luiz-172-189742.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u David Luiz</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-nen-tu-choi-real-de-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-chelsea-172-189734.html\">Hazard n\u00ean t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-voi-napoli-vi-hlv-sarri-172-189709.html\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u201cchuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d HLV Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3889","checkdouble":"189958"},{"date":"22:08 29/06","title":"Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Colombia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/arsenal-va-chelsea-theo-duoi-ngoi-sao-dt-colombia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh l\u00e0 Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea.</h2><h2>Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i James Rodriguez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i James Rodriguez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i James Rodriguez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/Arsenal-va-Chelsea-theo-duoi-James-Rodriguez-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>James Rodriguez nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 4 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc song t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, James Rodriguez v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Colombia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Colombia v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich, James \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y th\u00eam m\u1ed9t n\u0103m n\u1eefa theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n hai n\u0103m t\u1eeb Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u01a1\u0301i \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd Sky Sports \u0111\u00e3 xa\u0301c nh\u00e2\u0323n t\u00e2n\u00a0HLV Niko Kovac cu\u0309a Bayern Munich kh\u00f4ng co\u0301 k\u00ea\u0301 hoa\u0323ch s\u01b0\u0309 du\u0323ng James Rodriguez \u01a1\u0309 mu\u0300a gia\u0309i t\u01a1\u0301i. \u0110i\u00ea\u0300u na\u0300y \u0111\u00f4\u0300ng nghi\u0303a v\u01a1\u0301i vi\u00ea\u0323c t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cu\u0309a c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 ng\u01b0\u01a1\u0300i Colombia ta\u0323i s\u00e2n Allianz Arena g\u00e2\u0300n nh\u01b0 \u0111a\u0303 khe\u0301p la\u0323i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3 hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh l\u00e0 Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Real Madrid. V\u01a1\u0301i Chelsea, The Blues \u0111ang ti\u0301nh \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng ti\u0300m ng\u01b0\u01a1\u0300i thay th\u00ea\u0301 Willian trong tr\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng h\u01a1\u0323p c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 ng\u01b0\u01a1\u0300i Brazil quy\u00ea\u0301t t\u00e2m ra \u0111i, trong khi Arsenal c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c sau khi chia tay Jack Wilshere.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t James Rodriguez t\u1eeb Real v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Bayern Munich mua \u0111\u01b0\u0301t ti\u00ea\u0300n v\u00ea\u0323 26 tu\u00f4\u0309i v\u01a1\u0301i gia\u0301 35,2 tri\u00ea\u0323u euro n\u1ebfu H\u00f9m x\u00e1m mu\u1ed1n.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-va-arsenal-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-han-quoc-172-189762.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/mu-va-arsenal-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-va-arsenal-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-han-quoc-172-189762.html\">MU v\u00e0 Arsenal chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Ronaldo H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nMU v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Son Heung-Min r\u1eddi Tottenham, Sport 1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/doi-bong-cua-serie-a-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-sao-khung-arsenal-172-189741.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/doi-bong-cua-serie-a-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-sao-khung-arsenal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/doi-bong-cua-serie-a-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-sao-khung-arsenal-172-189741.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Serie A b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Arsenal</span><br>\r\nLazio mu\u1ed1n mua Aaron Ramsey trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Sergej Milinkovic-Savic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Serie A ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-muon-arsenal-rut-ruot-real-madrid-172-189735.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/19/hlv-emery-muon-arsenal-rut-ruot-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-muon-arsenal-rut-ruot-real-madrid-172-189735.html\">HLV Emery mu\u1ed1n Arsenal r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Lucas Vazquez c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3888","checkdouble":"189966"},{"date":"15:07 29/06","title":"HAGL th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Luka Modric cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hagl-chieu-mo-dong-huong-voi-luka-modric-de-va-hang-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL \u0111ang th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh th\u1ee9 hai cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a V-League 2018 mang t\u00ean Josip Zeba t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Croatia.</h2><h2>HAGL\u00a0th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c t\u00e2n binh\u00a0Josip Zeba cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Kim Jin-seo. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n HAGL.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Josip Zeba \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HAGL chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Josip Zeba \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Josip-Zeba-HAGL.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Josip Zeba\u00a0cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc sang giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2, \"G\u1ed7\" \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t thay th\u1ebf c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh. Sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Brazil Osmar thay th\u1ebf Rimario, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HAGL \u0111ang th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia Josip Zeba, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed1t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Kim Jin-seo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Josip Zeba sinh n\u0103m 1990, thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. Anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao 1m88 v\u00e0 t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Slovenia trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o NK Aluminij (m\u00f9a r\u1ed3i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 8 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Prva Liga 2018).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018, th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Josip Zeba th\u00ec hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V.League 2018.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 HAGL s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ngay v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, khi 'G\u1ed7' c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 17 di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 1/7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda HAGL, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh cho bi\u1ebft BHL \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Josip Zeba.\u00a0CLB s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Josip Zeba v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Vincent Bossou \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 9/7 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat-168-189842.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat-168-189842.html\">HAGL m\u1ea5t C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League v\u00ec \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a V-League sau khi \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\">HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3887","checkdouble":"189946"},{"date":"16:35 29/06","title":"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-khong-ngai-u19-thai-lan-o-ngay-ra-quan-u19-dna.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018.</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: center;\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan, Philippines, L\u00e0o, Singapore v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n U19 \u0110N\u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Gap-hang-lom,-DT-U19-Viet-Nam-dai-thang-tran-dau-tren-dat-Trung-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0110N\u00c1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u0169ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1eeb 3, 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea3.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang ta ch\u1ec9 thua k\u00e9m Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00ec c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u00e1ch quan chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, ho\u1eb7c ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng l\u00ean 'd\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n' cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng thua Th\u00e1i Lan. G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U15 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2017, Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 Th\u00e1i Lan, Australia \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c em khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho d\u00f9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p Th\u00e1i Lan, Indonesia hay Philippines&quot;, \u00f4ng Tu\u1ea5n 'con' n\u00f3i th\u00eam.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u01a1n 10 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp l\u00e0m quen t\u1ea1i Surabaya tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0110KV\u0110 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n l\u00fac 15h30 chi\u1ec1u 1/7 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018: (Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean VTV6)</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 1/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 3/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Philippines (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 5/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 L\u00e0o (SV\u0110 Joko Samudro)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 19h00, 7/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Indonesia (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- 15h30, 8/7, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; U19 Singapore (SV\u0110 Gelora Delta)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3886","checkdouble":"189953"},{"date":"15:25 29/06","title":"Matic n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c MU chi 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Fred?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/matic-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-52-trieu-bang-mua-fred.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nemanja Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Fred, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mua Fred v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Carrick gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 c\u00f2n Fellaini ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi hay kh\u00f4ng, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Fred c\u1ee7a Shakhtar Donetsk l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nemanja Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Fred h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nemanja Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Fred h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/matic-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-52-trieu-bang-mua-fred.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U mua Fred v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-cong-bo-tan-binh-fred-172-189182.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fred</span>, theo \u0111\u00f3 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Man \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecf ra trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Fred duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Paul Pogba s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFred \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil \u0111\u1ebfn Nga d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, song ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Matic \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Fred</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nemanja Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Fred, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matic an dinh chien thang tran MU vs Brighton\" title=\"Matic \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn MU vs Brighton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/matic-da-co-keo-voi-man-utd-tu-khi-con-la-quan-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Matic \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e2n binh Fred</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Fred. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f9ng tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap M.U t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Fred nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a M.U. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1eb9n nhau khi t\u1eadp trung \u1edf CLB s\u1ebd tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n th\u00eam, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t s\u1eb5n l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3885","checkdouble":"189944"},{"date":"15:43 29/06","title":"Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec \"ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1ea1\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/chelsea-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-tien-dao-la.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Moussa Marega c\u1ee7a Porto, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mali c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tottenham nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMorata \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 sau 1 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/juventus-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-172-185574.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Morata</span>, PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Moussa Marega c\u1ee7a Porto h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Moussa Marega c\u1ee7a Porto h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/Chelsea-muon-mua-Moussa-Marega-cua-Porto-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111ang c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Morata \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 11 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Morata n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Juventus ho\u1eb7c PSG ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Morata, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o thay th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi, h\u1ecd \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Fernando Llorente \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. Spurs \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n\u00a0m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Harry Kane.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Moussa Marega</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Moussa Marega c\u1ee7a Porto, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mali c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tottenham nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea va Tottenham muon co Marega\" title=\"Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Marega\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/chelsea-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-tien-dao-la.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Marega</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mali \u0111\u00e3 ghi 22 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 27 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u0110N, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Porto \u0111\u0103ng quang ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMoussa Marega r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, ngo\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eafm anh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, s\u00fat xa v\u00e0 ch\u1edbp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarega c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u euro, song b\u00e1o ch\u00ed B\u0110N kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n chi ra 28 tri\u1ec7u euro l\u00e0 Tottenham ho\u1eb7c Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEverton, West Ham v\u00e0 Schalke c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Marega, song r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea l\u00e0 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3884","checkdouble":"189945"},{"date":"16:15 29/06","title":"MU nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/mu-nhan-tin-buon-vu-hau-ve-trai-40-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Ryan Sessegnon c\u1ee7a Fulham \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Theo The Times, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U nh\u1eafm Ryan Sessegnon n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Jose Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Ashley Young \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u0103m nay Young \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, M.U c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho c\u1ef1u sao Aston Villa.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee5 MU mua Ryan Sessegnon Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u0103m b\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1ee5 MU mua Ryan Sessegnon Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u0103m b\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/5/mu-nhan-tin-buon-vu-hau-ve-trai-40-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ryan Sessegnon</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Luke Shaw, song \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Luke Shaw \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n, Mourinho c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Luke Shaw n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Young \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n Luke Shaw mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Ryan Sessegnon \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 2000 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 Ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Fulham th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRyan Sessegnon c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 8 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 49 tr\u1eadn. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i, c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ryan Sessegnon b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho MU</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Fulham b\u00e1n Ryan Sessegnon, M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fulham nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee5 MU mua Ryan Sessegnon Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u0103m b\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1ee5 MU mua Ryan Sessegnon Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u0103m b\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/22/Hau-ve-Ryan-Sessegnon-bi-HLV-Fulham-canh-bao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ryan Sessegnon mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-50-trieu-bang-mu-thoi-bay-moi-doi-thu-de-co-than-dong-anh-172-187645.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mua Ryan Sessegnon</span> c\u1ee7a Fulham \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Theo The Times, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 18, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u01b0u ti\u00ean ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Craven Cottage.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3883","checkdouble":"189949"},{"date":"16:35 29/06","title":"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u00e0 Tottenham v\u1ee5 \"Ronaldo H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/liverpool-muon-vuot-mat-mu-va-tottenham-vu-ronaldo-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Son Heung-Min c\u1ee7a Tottenham sau khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir t\u1eeb Lyon b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3, The Kop c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Son Heung-Min</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, The Kop quan t\u00e2m Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Liverpool \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 \u1edf ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Son Heung-Min thay Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Son Heung-Min thay Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/liverpool-muon-vuot-mat-mu-va-tottenham-vu-ronaldo-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Son Heung-Min</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLyon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng. Mua h\u1ee5t Nabil Fekir khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Metro, Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Son Heung-Min c\u1ee7a Tottenham sau khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir t\u1eeb Lyon b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3, The Kop c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Son Heung-Min ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 27 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-min om mat khoc sau tran thua Juventus\" title=\"Son Heung-min \u00f4m m\u1eb7t kh\u00f3c sau tr\u1eadn thua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/son-heungmin-khoc-nuc-no-tottenham-xung-dang-gianh-chien-thang-truoc-juventus.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool c\u00f3 Son Heung-min</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Son Heung-Min s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong c\u00f9ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-va-arsenal-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-han-quoc-172-189762.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal v\u00e0 M.U c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Son Heung-Min</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. V\u1edbi Tottenham, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3882","checkdouble":"189950"},{"date":"16:51 29/06","title":"Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/7/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jasper Cillessen mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jasper Cillessen kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca. Trong c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh 1 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga v\u00e0\u00a01 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Champions League, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng anh \u1edf c\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/9/10/ter-stegen-chan-thuong-cillessen-som-ra-mat-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jasper Cillessen \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 lu\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Marc-Andre ter Stegen khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 Barca \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ngay \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-thu-mon-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-liverpool-172-187430.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Jasper Cillessen c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jasper Cillessen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Kop l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karius, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn thua 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra t\u1eeb 25 \u0111\u1ebfn 30 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf Barca, song t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Cillessen v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3881","checkdouble":"189954"},{"date":"09:44 29/06","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n V-League b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra \u0111i sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/13/tai-em-bat-ngo-ra-di-sau-thanh-tich-te-hai-cua-sai-gon-fc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u2018t\u1ee5t d\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng phanh\u2019 v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean BXH, HLV T\u00e0i Em m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t.\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m<br>\r\n</span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng s\u1ed1c n\u00e0y, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t th\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL v\u00e0 SLNA v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra \u0111i sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra \u0111i sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/13/tai-em-bat-ngo-ra-di-sau-thanh-tich-te-hai-cua-sai-gon-fc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 28/6, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi CLB. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cCLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft n\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 HLV c\u00f2n non ngh\u1ec1 \u1edf V-League. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u nay t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chuy\u1ec7n chia tay ngay sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 gi\u1edd v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 r\u1ed3i. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u1ea3 quan trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec1 ra. Xin ch\u00fac anh em nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n theo d\u00f5i b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh em trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Tu\u1ea5n Phong \u0111\u00e3 thay m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi: \u201cAnh em ai c\u0169ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00ec sao ra n\u00f4ng n\u1ed7i n\u00e0y. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00ec m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ra \u0111i. S\u00e0i G\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i Em l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m, s\u1ed1ng h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed3ng, vui v\u1ebb n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng anh em trong \u0111\u1ed9i. CLB n\u00e0y v\u1ed1n r\u1ea5t l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00ec l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i Em c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n th\u1ee9 hai ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 HLV Marian Mihail c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia tay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-325-189774.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-325-189774.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: SLNA 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 mau ch\u00f3ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi-168-189359.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi-168-189359.html\">Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, HLV T\u00e0i Em t\u1ed1 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-168-189318.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-168-189318.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00ec l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua HAGL nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3880","checkdouble":"189935"}]}